posts.text:
Better is the only choice.
@fcbarcelona purest expression of footballing perfection meets the constant growth mindset of Mamba Mentality.

Millor és l’única opció.
La màxima expressió de la perfecció futbolística del @fcbarcelona conflueix amb l’actitud de creixement constant de la Mamba Mentality.

Mejor es la única opción.

posts.text: Nice finishes first. @janniksin takes home his second Grand Slam title. #WinningIsntForEveryone

media.ocrText: Jannik Sinner is turned towards the right side and is pictured making a fist as his eyes look upwards and his mouth is slightly opened. Sinner is wearing a black Nike hat, a green patterned shirt and a black Nike sweatband on his raised arm. The background of the tennis court is blurred. Micro graphics read “Jannik Sinner, Winner Grand Slam.”
White background with black text that reads “It’s hard to beat the nicest guy.” Micro graphics read “Jannik Sinner.”

Jannik Sinner is pictured with outstretched arms and both hands on his tennis racket in mid swing. His outstretched arms are actively engaged with his arm muscles and veins prominent. He is facing towards the left. Jannik Sinner is wearing a black Nike hat, a green patterned shirt, a black sweat band on his arm and black Nike shorts. The background of the onlooking crowd is blurred.

posts.text:
In their golden era.

@nielsvink sweeps wheelchair tennis quad across doubles and singles, @kiara.rodriguezec
claims victory in the long jump, and @jetze_plat dominates the road race.

#WinningIsntForEveryone #Paris2024
Return. Compete. Win. @arynasabalenka roared back to secure Grand Slam victory. #WinningIsntForEveryone

That’s one giant leap for humankind.

With a distance of 8.13 meters, @the.bladejumper secures his 4th straight @paralympics gold.

#WinningIsntForEveryone #Paris2024

Add another win to her story. 📖

A formidable rower, skier and cyclist, @oksanamasters just secured her 8th @paralympics gold with a win on the streets of Paris.

#WinningIsntForEveryone #Paris2024

2014 design. Modern day technology. You’re welcome.

The Kobe 9 Elite High Protro is available 8.23 on SNKRS in select regions. The Low makes its return on 9.19.

You can’t stop the reign.

There’s no argument, @dianataurasi’s resume is goated. She’s been one of the best players in the world for over two decades. A 6th gold medal would make her THE most decorated basketball player in @Olympics history.
